memory_hint:
get and set in TypeScript. <p>TypeScript uses getter/setter syntax that is like ECMAScript4/ActionScript3.</p>
<pre><code>class foo {
    private _bar: boolean = false;
    get bar(): boolean {
        return this._bar;
    }
    set bar(value: boolean) {
        this._bar = value;
    }
}
</code></
